        "## 2. Within-Subject Expertise Comparison\n",
        "\n",
        "    Generates a grouped bar chart comparing Novice vs.\n",
        "    Expert decoding accuracies. Includes scaled error bars and subgroup-specific significance percentages.\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
